學習規範 Course Policy
	    Include the attendance and contributions in class activities and discussions. Each class absence will be taken away 5 points from class participation score. Weekly reflection will be counted to demonstrate the students’ understanding status for the class work.      

評量方式 Grading


方法百分比%

其他 others:Oral report of “My values of moral and life”
10其他 others:Finish the apply form of the human research ethics committee
10其他 others:Oral report of “clinical ethics of healthcare issues”
20其他 others:Oral report and manuscript for the specific topic
