課程教材 Course Material
	    Required text book:
1. Beauchamp, T.L. & Childress, J.F. (2013). Principles of biomedical ethics. (7th ed.). New York: Oxford University Press.
2. Jonsen, A. R., Siegler, M., & Winslade, W. J. (2014). Clinical ethics. (8th ed.). USA: McGraw-Hill.    

參考書目 References
Recommended Books：
Beauchamp, T.L. & Childress, J.F. (2013). Principles of biomedical ethics. (7th ed.). New York: Oxford University Press.
Israel, M. (2014). Research ethics and integrity for social scientists: Beyond regulatory compliance. (2nd ed.). New York: SAGE Publications.
Jonsen, A. R., Siegler, M., & Winslade, W. J. (2015). Clinical ethics. (8th ed.). USA: McGraw-Hill.
Nichols-Casebolt, A. (2012). Research integrity and responsible conduct of research (Building social work research capacity). (1st ed.). New York: Oxford University Press.
Steneck, N. H. (2007). Introduction to the responsible conduct of research. (Revised ed.). Washington, D.C.: U. S. Government Printing Office.
Recommended Journals：
1. Hastings Center Report
2. Journal of Medical Ethics
3. Social Science Medicine
4. Nursing Ethics
5. Ethics and Law in Nursing Practice    

